ps://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.163.com%2Fnewview%2Fmovie%2Fcourseintro%3Fnewurl%3D%252Fspecial%252Fopencourse%252Fphilosophy-death.html&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedSvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=acb551b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://open.163.com/newview/movie/courseintro?newurl=%2Fspecial%2Fopencourse%2Fphilosophy-death.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n怕死其實係一件唔理性既事 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡體注意 <br />\nBTW 本身作者有出到書 英文版都好易入口 <br />\n有興趣Kindle <br />\n入面雖然話講哲學但佢用最顯淺既概念推理死係咩一件事 包括死後有無世界 有無靈魂 自我同一性同自殺道德問題等等"},{"pid":"9c0955a0c1a2d288700a70af60ff288d3913a074","tid":2434472,"uid":67428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6214ac14a292905012f4de497a1652b5d38fd36","tid":2434472,"uid":264838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6139de826cab69939cbe357c486d17c94c4199df","tid":2434472,"uid":335664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"個心會離一離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好驚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔敢面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T09:01:06.000Z","msg":"好事黎 證明你仲好想生存<br />\n我諗起會覺得唔太差 可以煩少好多野"},{"pid":"6e1aa351859e7d447baed0d331a7a98eb92d4651","tid":2434472,"uid":76221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T09:08:43.000Z","msg":"Why should I fear death?<br />\nIf I am, then death is not.<br />\nIf Death is, then I am not.<br />\nWhy should I fear that which can only exist when I do not?<br />\nLong time men lay oppressed with slavish fear.<br />\nReligious tyranny did domineer.<br />\nAt length the mighty one of Greece<br />\nBegan to assent the liberty of man."}]}